{"tid":1117101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你覺得人性本善定人性本惡?","createTime":"2019-04-20T12:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T05:50:24.000Z","uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9a82bba4cd7129b883a1391610507244f0899bb7","tid":1117101,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d5310fbc4eb362590eb169cc80197f09b15155","tid":1117101,"uid":10105,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:47:08.000Z","msg":"人性本惡<br />\nD細路細細個就識講大話，打交，爭玩具<br />\n雖則大多數係比物質引誘到<br />\n而慢慢長大先會因法律，道德去束縛左個人"},{"pid":"5ba47dd7cfed26001e0187a0fda00dad905e8b30","tid":1117101,"uid":177013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"Why not both？"},{"pid":"c5ee3197cdf53c9dbe157c032635db2d71d1fe94","tid":1117101,"uid":154608,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得冇分善惡，純粹係一張白紙，本能只有生存，其他都係社會造成。"},{"pid":"2a34b5bff3146aa896723ea59de0646556fd9629","tid":1117101,"uid":249519,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:58:11.000Z","msg":"人性嘅本質係利益同生存 儒家思想嘅性善/性惡論已經落後 人性應該係達爾文嘅物競天擇適者生存"},{"pid":"17ef71da52dcf50d956cfd4f514a6dc989879bc6","tid":1117101,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"有一點好有趣<br />\n<br />\n有好多 電影/電視劇, 都會講一個壞人/殺手 意外失億<br />\n但 壞人/殺手 失億之後, 就會變左好人, 忘記自己做過既壞事<br />\n當最後結局記得自己既壞事之後, 都會堅持做好人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是否代表人善本性??<br />\n定係D 導演 老作??"},{"pid":"6915733e376626bda527eee7e8375c203fcfa6c8","tid":1117101,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"本無善惡"},{"pid":"d4a2a9cd4d5335d26e13c7f071e3f207b4b348cb","tid":1117101,"uid":2784,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.tw.observer/images/Ybovfnq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.tw.observer%2Fimages%2FYbovfnq.jpg&h=af84c8c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cb66c08fc099640f8c631f98bca4b4f5e5d154f","tid":1117101,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"何為善？何為惡？<br />\n善惡都只係世人按自身利益標準而訂立。<br />\n世間上跟本唔存在善惡，只有因果。"},{"pid":"1c93351872c91d14bfb6a81400af5bf54d914d75","tid":1117101,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"一定係惡，唔洗諗<br />\n你試下餓2個b一段時間，同時間放入一間房，只有一支奶（你必須當佢地已經識拎黎飲）<br />\n你覺得佢地會好禮讓咁俾另一個飲先，搶住飲，定叻到知另一半餓黎個開心share?"},{"pid":"26336f4a6898c36598ba455c8e46e17c7d3b32ff","tid":1117101,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有善 <br />\n<br />\n就會有惡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有惡<br />\n<br />\n就會有善"},{"pid":"d30054464f9eb2d334ee33c443ff62c4a7ac8ae7","tid":1117101,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"一個善既人都會被學校, 社會, 職場<br />\n改變成惡既人"},{"pid":"738fbdf6faaddb011c3294d9e3c7859492ae9bef","tid":1117101,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"同自己無直接利益衝突時好多人會選擇善<br />\n一影響到自身利益全部變惡"},{"pid":"fb28dcfe926793665cce7b8bba5284fd76d7efcb","tid":1117101,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30054464f9eb2d334ee33c443ff62c4a7ac8ae7","tid":1117101,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"一個善既人都會被學校, 社會, 職場<br />\n改變成惡既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />善根本生存唔到"},{"pid":"4efd229fd9c772559a201f4843d6e409a9e4cb36","tid":1117101,"uid":15916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:43:25.000Z","msg":"好難做到完全嘅&lsquo;本&rsquo;<br />\n我覺得係基因主導"},{"pid":"5bbdb76c7c0fa6d5f520684c977012fd5af86562","tid":1117101,"uid":54737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:43:27.000Z","msg":"只係每個人既選擇"},{"pid":"ab60cb3792dd98ea16e67650bad8800b896d7c9b","tid":1117101,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:46:54.000Z","msg":"一定係性本惡<br />\n屌你老母hk01<br />\n人係以自身利益為先，就算滿足咗自己，淨低嘅利益未必會分享比人，仲邊可能會顧埋其他人？hk01死全家<br />\n而加我地嘅善只係維持社會秩序而存在，一但冇咗政府 社會條件 法律，你覺得你仲會唔會去保持善良一面？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f4ee474d29605faef91e531dd6c8b463e56367","tid":1117101,"uid":66810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"惡"},{"pid":"377119787b89f6b6193684809a1d084b3614007d","tid":1117101,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得善惡只係在於人的睇法<br />\n本來就好難分清楚<br />\n劫富濟貧係善定惡？<br />\n如果被劫的財係不義之財或者係正當財產<br />\n又會唔會有影響呢？"},{"pid":"b3b3e6c7e7074cd51a76f51e4009869181bda606","tid":1117101,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:43:01.000Z","msg":"點解人有分善惡其他動物無？"},{"pid":"59c71cf2f3a0479a556db16a30284befaa28c24d","tid":1117101,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b3e6c7e7074cd51a76f51e4009869181bda606","tid":1117101,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:43:01.000Z","msg":"點解人有分善惡其他動物無？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"你點知其他動物無？"},{"pid":"a4800705960d8a3b30868ae860f06e471ae46e60","tid":1117101,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c71cf2f3a0479a556db16a30284befaa28c24d","tid":1117101,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b3e6c7e7074cd51a76f51e4009869181bda606","tid":1117101,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T20:43:01.000Z","msg":"點解人有分善惡其他動物無？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T03:36:05.000Z","msg":"你點知其他動物無？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":